{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Stormwater Fuses the genres of Classic Shooting Games with Point and Click Adventure.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Now in exile, the only work left for Prussy the Sailor is at a parish in the haunted countryside of a foreign land. With his old friend Priest Grail, together they must guide the spirit of their town and lift the many curses that plague the continent- or else fall, packed down into dark earth.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349770/extras/RvR6VP.gif?t=1735578634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Develop</strong>\u00a0relationships with the strangers of the continent, as you strive to fulfill your duty for the church, guarding the spiritual welfare of the town of Perinthia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349770/extras/S7_OKF.gif?t=1735578634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Investigate</strong> dark curses that range from spirits haunting forgotten homes, to the cruel\u00a0possessions of entire towns, and even the ineffable horrors buried deep beneath the earth.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349770/extras/JXYG3Q.gif?t=1735578634\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slay</strong> hordes of darkness. Whatever comes their way, Priest\u00a0Grail and Prussy the Sailor are always ready to shoot, kick, burn, slice, and blow to pieces their enemies. Curses or otherwise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Landed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/publi